data.description: This spacious condo offers breathtaking views of Mount Rainier, Narrows Passage, and the Narrows Bridge with elegant hardwood floors throughout and large windows that flood the interior with natural light. The main living areas are conveniently situated on the main level for comfortable daily living. The lower level stands out with a separate entrance and a fully-equipped kitchen, making it ideal for a mother-in-law suite or guest space. The spacious 2-car garage has a 2nd W/D and large storage room. Nature enthusiasts will appreciate the wooded trail that leads to the beach. Walk to the Clubhouse with an outdoor pool. Convenience and natural beauty in a scenic living space only 10 min to downtown and easy access to hwy 16!
